  "body": "<h1 data-v-189c2ea9=\"\" class=\"title\">𝗢𝘃𝗲𝗿𝘃𝗶𝗲𝘄</h1>\n<font size=\"3\"> ◼ It's just a rework of the Minecraft hub in dark mode with a few small changes. \n<br>◼ It's something I do only as a hobby for my own Minecraft, so I don't have any more versions of this pack <br> &nbsp; &nbsp; (Or maybe I do, but I don't remember where I kept it). \n<br>◼ For now, it is only compatible with the vanilla version of Minecraft Java. </font>\n\n<h1 data-v-189c2ea9=\"\" class=\"title\"> 𝗦𝗰𝗿𝗲𝗲𝗻𝘀𝗵𝗼𝘁𝘀</h1>\n- Note: Use Complementary Shaders to take all screenshots.<br><br>\n- Note: Some details are available only on 1.21.5 version.<br><br>\n<img src= \"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/l3XQI1J3/images/8dead83d43e4671f76dfdea8561b8c756ced2955.jpeg\" alt=\"Title\" width=\"1000\" height=\"400\"><br><br>\n<img src= \"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/l3XQI1J3/images/281c986b1e16f788ea46d08e83d1dd9a85ca1d0b.jpeg\" alt=\"Title\" width=\"1000\" height=\"400\"><br><br>\n<img src= \"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/l3XQI1J3/images/7a4337dfe69ddf5813f0d3bf69ad19c432914e94.jpeg\" alt=\"Title\" width=\"1000\" height=\"400\"><br><br>\n<img src= \"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/l3XQI1J3/images/32c762af456be0b64755522ac8a6c1f6077352aa.jpeg\" alt=\"Title\" width=\"1000\" height=\"400\"><br><br>\n<img src= \"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/l3XQI1J3/images/387af8f90c43ac760eb87128d0f559d09f0529c1.jpeg\" alt=\"Title\" width=\"1000\" height=\"400\"><br><br>\n<img src= \"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/l3XQI1J3/images/1c81c74189532a54476780787ce3a7f18b0b8acf.jpeg\" alt=\"Title\" width=\"1000\" height=\"400\"><br><br>\n<img src= \"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/l3XQI1J3/images/46147a4b1965470d5aa0364e5e74f5a3f908782a.jpeg\" alt=\"Title\" width=\"1000\" height=\"400\"><br><br>\n<img src= \"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/l3XQI1J3/images/9c15247a72e0943b135bd5702d34e04140ff2eff.jpeg\" alt=\"Title\" width=\"1000\" height=\"400\"><br><br>\n<img src= \"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/l3XQI1J3/images/d2c5924e440dfe76505